        Retrieve a value by a Expression instance.

        V - type of result.

      • get

        <V> V get(String key)
        Retrieve a value by a column or alias name.
        Type Parameters:
        V - type of result.
        Parameters:
        key - the alias or column name used in the query
        Returns:
